{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, using deep learning technologies to recognize and separate human voices from background noise (Al-Barhan et al. 2021) is also a noteworthy direction.",
    "Furthermore, future research should also focus on the characteristics of noise in different environments (such as outdoors, inside vehicles, public places, etc.)",
    "(Dubey et al. 2022), and explore how to adjust noise suppression strategies adaptively to suit these specific environments.",
    "(4) Dialect speech emotion recognition: Investigating the emotional information contained in dialect speech is essential for creating personalized services and improving user experience (Aljuhani et al. 2021).",
    "It can not only augment the understanding of dialect culture but also further perceive users' emotions."
  ]
}